      <title>前高盛银行家因加纳贿赂案而抗争引渡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/ex-goldman-banker-asante-berko-fights-extradition-over-alleged-ghana-bribery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 前银行家对英国将其引渡至美国的决定提出上诉，他面临在该投资银行工作期间贿赂加纳官员的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/ex-goldman-banker-asante-berko-fights-extradition-over-alleged-ghana-bribery</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其为充满焦虑的新政策时代调整利率信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/turkish-central-bank-raises-inflation-outlook-that-shapes-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其通胀终于接近顶峰，但央行的担忧依然存在，这种不安可能会使利率在更长时间内保持在较高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/turkish-central-bank-raises-inflation-outlook-that-shapes-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 08:04:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
